{"tid":1222301,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"香港人未曾試過企到咁硬","createTime":"2019-06-14T11:41:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-14T15:41:06.000Z","uid":249376,"like":79,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"d203990b57851ed73c32b297adad60d3129dbebb","tid":1222301,"uid":249376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T11:41:26.000Z","msg":"即使無視103萬民意硬推<br />\n即使被暴力鎮壓市民和平示威<br />\n即使有機會留案底拉去坐監<br />\n即使面對一堆5毛港豬廢老批鬥<br />\n即使港共政府宣布暫緩分化民調聲音<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">香港人都從來未試過好似依家咁照樣企硬反擊<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\">正如時代雜誌標題所言：</span>香港人正站於全球自由之戰的前線<br />\n<br />\n保衛香港憲法之戰<br />\n６．１６遊行<br />\n不撤！<br />\n不退！<br />\n向惡法說不！<br />\n向林鄭說Fuck！<br />\n</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FJbS2Aq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFJbS2Aq.jpg&h=8b3762ef&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0DNZHAt.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0DNZHAt.jpg&h=ac812565&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f195c3c4532bb181d988763bdb2bd9c9867781ca","tid":1222301,"uid":32380,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T11:42:17.000Z","msg":"每一個出嚟遊行 集會嘅我都覺得佢地型到痴線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b22e28e787af6dc91aa1a6d96665a5ff5571ec1c","tid":1222301,"uid":249376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T11:47:46.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"e9c39851cf8e26d0be4c38038ab623d3f0d16012","tid":1222301,"uid":249376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T11:56:07.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"274e27010cb586c204e16cc36990bd0ab4ba75df","tid":1222301,"uid":199659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T12:06:54.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"893617a1cd3ec91cb0c096df432e432a1f17b56b","tid":1222301,"uid":249376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-0